text.section:
As a prerequisite to the issuance of a facility permit, the Department shall require an applicant:
To provide evidence of financial ability to properly establish, operate, and maintain a controlled hazardous substance facility;
To file with the Department acceptable evidence of a bond or other security that the Department requires under § 7-242 of this subtitle;
To agree to permit access to the controlled hazardous substance facility for the purposes of any inspection permitted or required under this subtitle; and
To pay the permit fee assessed under § 7-237 of this subtitle.
